observe.desc:
[
{A mysterious worn-out machinery used for operations. }
]

[
{This machine was designed to lift back the skull and destroy nerve tissue safely and efficiently..}
]

[
{Many of those who underwent an operation inside the machinery have found rest and became healthy again.}
]

      [
      {Those who answered "Yes" to the question, "Do you love your city?" were deemed cured. Those who answered "No," weren’t allowed to be discharged.
The longer the machinery is used, the better the employees become.}
    ]

[
{Also, the longer you use it, the faster the question changes.}
]
